      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/01/the-best-we-can-hope-for/#comment-16238"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-03-20T03:35:00-04:00">Friday, March 20, 2009 at 3:35 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made this tonight alongside a red pepper and chicken stirfry.  My mother pronounced it &#8220;sublime.&#8221;  Needless to say, it&#8217;s definitely going to become a regular part of our rotation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-16238' data-commentid="16238" data-postid="1028" data-belowelement="comment-16238" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Caredwen" aria-label='Reply to Caredwen'>Reply</a>    </div>
