      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/01/the-best-we-can-hope-for/#comment-16239"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-03-28T02:43:00-04:00">Saturday, March 28, 2009 at 2:43 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made this for dinner tonight with the fresh head of cabbage my mom gave me from her garden. It was sublime. Totally delicious and awesome! Thank you!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-16239' data-commentid="16239" data-postid="1028" data-belowelement="comment-16239" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Karen" aria-label='Reply to Karen'>Reply</a>    </div>
