    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Tried this last night &#8211; squeezed in a whole lime and added fresh ginger, garlic, and green onion. It was so great and ended up tasting a little like pad thai! 1/2 cabbage was the perfect portion to serve two people. </p>
<p>Also added 1/2 cup of brown rice once it was plated to help soak up the extra juices and add some more texture. </p>
<p>Sprinkled shaved roasted almonds on top for a little crunch!</p>
